BunnyCake - AUTO CAKE YIELD GENERATION AND BUYBACK TOKEN
Simply hold your $BunnyCake and earn $CAKE. We've also added awesome features like Auto-Boost and Hyper Buy-Back!

14% tax, 7% is used to purchase CAKE which is automatically paid out in dividends to holders automatically.

6% is split between buy back mechanism and team/marketing fund. Marketing Fund which is 2% can be used in extreme circumstances to correct market volatility.

Liquidity Locked: 70% - Unlock Date : 6 months.

Total Supply: 1 quadrilion.
